<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>NakamaStream - En Desarrollo</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Bienvenido a NakamaStream, tu futura plataforma de streaming favorita">
    <meta property="og:title" content="NakamaStream - Próximamente">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Prepárate para una experiencia de streaming única con NakamaStream">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/168317328?s=200&v=4">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://nakamastream.lat/">
    <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
    <meta name="twitter:title" content="NakamaStream - Próximamente">
    <meta name="twitter:description" content="Prepárate para una experiencia de streaming única con NakamaStream">
    <meta name="twitter:image" content="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/168317328?s=200&v=4">
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.6.0/css/all.min.css">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'custom-red': '#ff6b6b',
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'bounce-slow': 'bounce 3s infinite',
                        'pulse-slow': 'pulse 4s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.6, 1) infinite',
                        'loading-wave': 'loadingWave 1.5s ease-in-out infinite',
                    },
                    keyframes: {
                        loadingWave: {
                            '0%, 100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)' },
                            '50%': { transform: 'translateY(-15px)' },
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>

<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-100 to-gray-200 min-h-screen flex flex-col">
    <main class="flex-grow flex flex-col items-center justify-center p-8 text-center">
        <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white rounded-xl shadow-2xl p-8">
            <div class="mb-8">
                <img src="https://github.com/NakamaStream/Resources/raw/main/NakamStream-logo-HD-removebg.png?raw=true"
                    alt="NakamaStream Logo" class="w-56 h-56 mx-auto animate-bounce-slow" />
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-custom-red mb-6">NakamaStream</h1>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6">¡Estamos creando algo extraordinario!</h2>
            <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-10">Muy pronto, NakamaStream te ofrecerá una experiencia de streaming inigualable. Prepárate para disfrutar de tu contenido favorito como nunca antes.</p>
            
            <div class="flex justify-center space-x-6 mb-10">
                <div class="w-20 h-20 loading-box bg-custom-red rounded-lg animate-loading-wave"></div>
                <div class="w-20 h-20 loading-box bg-custom-red rounded-lg animate-loading-wave" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;"></div>
                <div class="w-20 h-20 loading-box bg-custom-red rounded-lg animate-loading-wave" style="animation-delay: 0.4s;"></div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="w-full max-w-md mx-auto progress-container bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 shadow-inner">
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-4">Progreso estimado:</p>
                <div class="w-full bg-gray-300 rounded-full h-6 overflow-hidden">
                    <div class="bg-custom-red h-6 rounded-full transition-all duration-1000 ease-out" style="width: 100%"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-10 space-y-6">
                <div>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-3">Mantente informado, únete a nuestra comunidad:</p>
                    <a href="https://discord.gg/nakamastream"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-custom-red text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-red-500 transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fab fa-discord fa-lg mr-3"></i>
                        Unirse al Discord
                    </a>
                </div>
                
                <div>
                    <p class="text-xl text-gray-800 mb-3">Explora nuestro progreso:</p>
                    <a href="/releases" target="_blank"
                        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 bg-custom-red text-white text-lg font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-red-500 transition duration-300">
                        <i class="fas fa-history fa-lg mr-3"></i>
                        Ver Historial de Releases
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </main>
</body>

</html>
